{%- comment -%}
/**
 * Frame Geometry Sheet Section
 * 
 * A comprehensive Shopify Liquid section for displaying bicycle frame geometry specifications
 * with interactive tabbed interface, multi-language support, and responsive design.
 * 
 * CORE FUNCTIONALITY:
 * - Interactive tabbed interface for different frame types (Step Through, Low Step, High Step, Mountain, Carbon)
 * - Dynamic frame geometry visualization with customizable images
 * - Detailed geometry measurements table with size variations (S, M, L, XL)
 * - Multi-language content support (German, French, Finnish, English)
 * - Responsive design with mobile-optimized layout
 * - Touch-friendly swipe navigation for mobile devices
 * 
 * TECHNICAL IMPLEMENTATION:
 * - Uses Liquid templating for dynamic content rendering
 * - JavaScript for tab switching and mobile responsiveness
 * - CSS for styling and responsive behavior
 * - Conditional rendering based on frame type and language
 * 
 * SHOPIFY INTEGRATION:
 * - Section-based architecture compatible with Shopify theme customizer
 * - Block-based content system for flexible configuration
 * - Settings schema for admin panel customization
 * - Multi-language support using Shopify's localization features
 * 
 * RELATED FILES:
 * - snippets/frame-size-table.liquid - Renders geometry measurement tables
 * - snippets/image.liquid - Handles responsive image rendering (if used)
 * 
 * LAYOUT OPTIONS:
 * - Tabbed interface with customizable tab labels
 * - Two-column layout (image + table) on desktop
 * - Single-column stacked layout on mobile
 * - Configurable frame type presets (Trekking, Mountain, City)
 * - Custom image upload support for each frame type
 * 
 * RESPONSIVE DESIGN:
 * - Desktop: Side-by-side image and table layout
 * - Mobile: Stacked layout with horizontal scrolling for images
 * - Touch-optimized navigation with swipe hints
 * - Adaptive table sizing for mobile screens
 * 
 * ACCESSIBILITY:
 * - Keyboard navigation support for tabs
 * - Semantic HTML structure
 * - Screen reader friendly table headers
 * - Focus management for interactive elements
 * 
 * CUSTOMIZATION OPTIONS:
 * - Multi-language section titles
 * - Frame type selection (step_through, low_step, high_step, mountain, carbon)
 * - Custom image uploads for each frame type
 * - Mobile-specific image optimization
 * - Geometry measurement customization per size
 * - Show/hide specific sizes (S, XL) based on frame type
 * 
 * MULTI-LANGUAGE SUPPORT:
 * - German (de): Comprehensive geometry terminology
 * - French (fr): Full translation support
 * - Finnish (fi): Complete localization
 * - English (en): Default language support
 * - Fallback to French for unsupported locales
 * 
 * BROWSER COMPATIBILITY:
 * - Modern browsers with CSS Grid and Flexbox support
 * - Touch event support for mobile devices
 * - Smooth scrolling and animations
 * - Progressive enhancement approach
 * 
 * PERFORMANCE CONSIDERATIONS:
 * - Lazy loading for images
 * - Efficient DOM manipulation
 * - Minimal JavaScript footprint
 * - Optimized CSS for fast rendering
 * 
 * USE CASES:
 * - E-bike and bicycle product pages
 * - Technical specification displays
 * - Product comparison interfaces
 * - Mobile-first product catalogs
 * 
 * DEFAULT PRESETS:
 * - Includes default geometry data for common frame types
 * - Pre-configured size variations (S, M, L, XL)
 * - Standard measurement categories (15 different measurements)
 * - Responsive image placeholders
 */
